-- PGNiG to Spend $31 Million on Shale Gas Exploration in Poland, rp.pl Says
-- Dorota Bartyzel
-- 2010-07-09T05:35:30Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-09/pgnig-to-spend-31-million-on-shale-gas-exploration-in-poland-rp-pl-says.html

          
          
             Polskie Gornictwo Naftowe i
Gazownictwo SA  will spend more than 100 million zloty ($31
million) on searching for shale gas in Poland in 2010 and
increase the expenditure in coming years, rp.pl reported, citing
Deputy Chief Executive Officer  Waldemar Wojcik .  
 To contact the reporter on this story:
